title: Don't Do Me Dirty
itunes:title: Don't Do Me Dirty
description:
Today on the show we opened up the phone lines to see if our listeners have ever been done wrong by their close friend after accusations came out about Ryan Henry sleeping with his best friends baby mom. Also, we opened up the phone lines to here some of our listeners stories about their Karen encounters and we had listeners nominate for Donkey of the Day.
